==潛在適居帶狀況==
{{Main|適居帶}}
在[[天文學|天文學]]和[[天體生物學|天體生物學]]，[[適居帶|適居帶]]是圍繞一顆[[恆星|恆星]]的特定區域，在這區域內的[[行星|行星]]有足夠的大氣壓力去維持地面上的液態水。<ref>{{cite web |title=VPL Glossary |url=http://vpl.astro.washington.edu/epo/glossary.html |publisher=washington.edu }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://science.nasa.gov/headlines/y2003/02oct_goldilocks.htm |title=The Goldilocks Zone |date=2 October 2003 |publisher=[[NASA|NASA]] |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090714102410/http://science.nasa.gov/headlines/y2003/02oct_goldilocks.htm |archivedate=2009-07-14}}</ref>

潛在適居行星是位於[[適居帶|適居帶]]的[[類地行星|類地行星]]，條件大致上與地球類似，因此有機會支持[[生命|生命]]。 

在2013年11月4日，基於[[克卜勒太空望遠鏡|''開普勒''太空任務]]資料，天文學家報稱[[銀河系|銀河系]]內有多達四百億顆[[類地行星|類地行星]]在圍繞[[類太陽恆星|類太陽恆星]]和[[紅矮星|紅矮星]]的[[適居帶|適居帶]]內運行，<ref name="NYT-20131104">{{cite news |last=Overbye |first=Dennis |title=Far-Off Planets Like the Earth Dot the Galaxy |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/11/05/science/cosmic-census-finds-billions-of-planets-that-could-be-like-earth.html |date=4 November 2013 |work=[[New_York_Times|New York Times]] |accessdate=5 November 2013 }}</ref><ref name="PNAS-20131031">{{cite journal |display-authors=1 |last1=Petigura |first1=Erik A. |last2=Howard |first2=Andrew W. |last3=Marcy |first3=Geoffrey W. |title=Prevalence of Earth-size planets orbiting Sun-like stars |url=http://www.pnas.org/content/early/2013/10/31/1319909110 |date=31 October 2013 |journal=[[Proceedings_of_the_National_Academy_of_Sciences_of_the_United_States_of_America|Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences of the United States of America]] |doi=10.1073/pnas.1319909110 |accessdate=5 November 2013 |arxiv=1311.6806 |bibcode=2013PNAS..11019273P |archive-date=2013-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131109010831/http://www.pnas.org/content/early/2013/10/31/1319909110 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 當中一百一十億可能是圍繞[[類太陽恆星|類太陽恆星]]運行。<ref name="LATimes-20131104">{{cite news |last=Khan |first=Amina |title=Milky Way may host billions of Earth-size planets |url=http://www.latimes.com/science/la-sci-earth-like-planets-20131105,0,2673237.story |date=4 November 2013 |work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]] |accessdate=5 November 2013 |archive-date=2014-02-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140205055450/http://www.latimes.com/science/la-sci-earth-like-planets-20131105,0,2673237.story |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2015年，有評論推斷太陽系外行星[[開普勒62f|開普勒62f]]、[[開普勒186f|開普勒186f]]和[[開普勒442b|開普勒442b]]可能是潛在適居的最佳候選。<ref name=centauridreams>{{cite web |url=http://www.centauri-dreams.org/?p=32470 |title=A Review of the Best Habitable Planet Candidates |author=Paul Gilster, Andrew LePage |date=30 January 2015 |publisher=Centauri Dreams, Tau Zero Foundation |accessdate=24 July 2015 |archive-date=2019-12-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191213082931/https://www.centauri-dreams.org/2015/01/30/a-review-of-the-best-habitable-planet-candidates/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 它們分別遠在1200、490和1120[[光年|光年]]以外，當中，[[開普勒186f|開普勒186f]]與地球的大小最相似，半徑是地球的1.2倍，而且位於一顆[[紅矮星|紅矮星]]的[[適居帶|適居帶]]外緣。

