==曾經候選==
* [[HD_85512_b|HD 85512 b]]起初被認為有可能適居，<ref name="Kaltenegger2011">{{cite journal |title=A Habitable Planet around HD 85512? |first=L. |last=Kaltenegger |first2=S. |last2=Udry |first3=F. |last3=Pepe |display-authors=1 |date=2011|arxiv=1108.3561 |bibcode=2011arXiv1108.3561K}}</ref><ref name="old1">{{cite press release |last=Mendez |first=Abel |title=Five Potential Habitable Exoplanets Now |url=http://phl.upr.edu/press-releases/fivepotentialhabitableexoplanetsnow |date=1 August 2012 |publisher=Planetary Habitability Laboratory @ UPR Arecibo |accessdate=4 June 2015}}</ref> 但對適居帶邊界的更新模型把這行星置於HZ內則，<ref name="Kopparapu2013">{{cite journal |title=Habitable Zones Around Main-Sequence Stars: New Estimates |url=https://archive.org/details/arxiv-1404.5292 |first=Ravi kumar |last=Kopparapu |first2=Ramses |last2=Ramirez |first3=James F. |last3=Kasting |first4=Vincent |last4=Eymet |first5=Tyler D. | last5=Robinson |first6=Suvrath | last6=Mahadevan |first7=Ryan C. | last7=Terrien |first8=Shawn | last8=Domagal-Goldman |first9=Victoria | last9=Meadows |first10=Rohit | last10=Deshpande |display-authors=1 |date=2013|arxiv=1301.6674 |bibcode=2013ApJ...765..131K|doi = 10.1088/0004-637X/765/2/131 }}</ref><ref name="newHZ">{{cite press release |last=Mendez |first=Abel |title=A New Habitable Zone |url=http://phl.upr.edu/press-releases/anewhabitablezone |date=29 January 2013 |publisher=Planetary Habitability Laboratory @ UPR Arecibo |accessdate=4 June 2015 |archive-date=2019-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191211194253/http://phl.upr.edu/press-releases/anewhabitablezone |dead-url=yes }}</ref> 它現時己被考慮為不適居。<ref name="PHL"/>

* [[開普勒69c|開普勒69c]]經歷了類似的歷程，雖然起初被相信有可能適居，<ref name="Barclay2013">{{cite journal |title=A super-Earth-sized planet orbiting in or near the habitable zone around Sun-like star |url=https://archive.org/details/arxiv-1304.4941 |first1=Thomas |display-authors=etal  |last1=Barclay  |date=2013|arxiv=1304.4941 |bibcode=2013ApJ...768..101B|doi = 10.1088/0004-637X/768/2/101 }}</ref> 但很快就被認識到這行星更可能是類似金星，<ref name="Kane2013">{{cite journal |title=A Potential Super-Venus in the Kepler-69 System |first=Stephen R. |last=Kane |first2=Thomas |last2=Barclay |first3=Dawn M. |last3=Gelino |display-authors=1 |date=2013|arxiv=1305.2933 |bibcode=2013ApJ...770L..20K|doi = 10.1088/2041-8205/770/2/L20 }}</ref> 亦因此不再被考慮為適居。<ref name="PHL"/>

* 同樣地，[[鯨魚座τf|鯨魚座τf]]起初被考慮為有可能適居，<ref name="taucet">{{cite press release |last=Mendez |first=Abel |title=Two Nearby Habitable Worlds? |url=http://phl.upr.edu/press-releases/twonearbyhabitableworlds |date=28 December 2012 |publisher=Planetary Habitability Laboratory @ UPR Arecibo |accessdate=4 June 2015}}</ref> 但對適居帶的改進模型把這行星置於適居帶外緣以外，因此它現在被考慮為不適居。<ref name="PHL"/>

* [[KOI-1686.01|KOI-1686.01]]在2011年被發現之後，曾經被考慮為單一最有可能適合人類居住的系外行星，直至2015年，美國太空總署證實是誤測。<ref>{{cite web|title=Kepler Candidate Overview Page: KOI-1686.01|url=http://exoplanetarchive.ipac.caltech.edu/cgi-bin/DisplayOverview/nph-DisplayOverview?objname=KOI-1686.01|website=NASA Exoplanet Archive|publisher=NASA Exoplanet Science Institute|accessdate=28 December 2015|archive-date=2015-01-11|archive-url=https://archive.is/20150111223510/http://exoplanetarchive.ipac.caltech.edu/cgi-bin/DisplayOverview/nph-DisplayOverview?objname=KOI-1686.01|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

